                  <msItem>
                     <p>
                        <pb n="615"/> Convention between the church of <orgName key="org_103001">Kirkestal</orgName> and the church of the
                  <orgName key="org_103019">Holy Trinity, York</orgName>, by which the church of Kirkestal agrees to pay annually 20s.
                  as compensation for tithes which they were accustomed to have from the lands which the monks of
                  Kirkestal hold in the parish of <placeName key="place_103253">Ledes</placeName>, viz. 4 carucates of land in
                  <placeName key="place_103200">West Hadigleia (Haddlesey)</placeName>, half in <placeName key="place_103200">Est Hadigleia</placeName>, 
                  2 carucates in <placeName key="place_103050">West Alretuna</placeName>, one bovate in <placeName key="place_103051">East Alretun</placeName>, 
                  the assart of <placeName type="minor">Sinleia</placeName>, of <placeName type="minor">Mideleia</placeName>, 
                  le <placeName type="minor">Enclov</placeName>, <placeName type="minor">Westrod[aid]</placeName> 
                        <placeName key="place_103088">the vale of Bramleia</placeName>.
                  Witn. <persName>
                           <forename>Richard</forename> abbot of Fountains</persName> etc.
                  (<origDate notBefore="1133" notAfter="1143" precision="low">c. 1133-43</origDate>.) 
                  . </p>
